Understanding Angular Versioning

1.  AngularJs (Angular 1)
2.  Angular 2 --> Complete Rewrite : Released in 2016
3.  Angular 4
4.  Angular 5
5.  Angular 6
6.  Angular 7
7.  Angular 8
8.  Angular 9
9.  Angular 10
10. Angular 11
11. Angular 12
New Version of Angular is released after every 6 Months


Updating npm
    npm install -g npm

Updating CLI:
    npm uninstall -g angular-cli @angular/cli 
    npm cache verify 
    npm install -g @angular/cli 

Help Command:
    ng help --> this will show the list of command that you can run on angular CLI
    ng [commmand] --help -> to get the info of the Specefic command

Creating a new Project:
    ng new my-first-angular-project

To run the Development Server:
    ng server
    ng server --port